## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and reports, which may not cover all aspects of bail reform or reflect the most recent changes in legislation. Additionally, the effectiveness of proposed reforms can vary by jurisdiction, and the implementation of risk assessment tools may have its own set of challenges and biases. Further empirical research is needed to evaluate the long-term impacts of these reforms on reducing disparities in the justice system.

